def transform_data(input_list):
    output_list = []
    for sublist in input_list:
        # Filter out empty strings and split the comma-separated names if any
        filtered = [s.split(',') for s in sublist if s]
        # Flatten the list and swap the order if it was last, first
        names = [name.strip() for sub in filtered for name in (sub[1], sub[0]) if len(sub) == 2] if filtered else [name for name in sublist if name]
        output_list.append(names)
    return output_list
